  <scopecontent id="aspace_a849ddbae8a1785bf83d7f997c59d2b8">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Collection consists of approximately 1000 stereographs of Watkins Glen and Havana Glen in New York State from the period 1860-1910. Most images are from the 1870s. Collection arranged by photographic company.</p>  </scopecontent>
